title: Prestige Lamborghini Super Trofeo Series Racing Drivers (Audio)
itunes:title: Prestige Lamborghini Super Trofeo Series Racing Drivers (Audio)
description:
(Bloomberg) -- Taking Stock with Kathleen Hays and Pimm Fox. GUEST: The Lamborghini Super Trofeo Racing Series Prestige drivers, Trent Hindman and David Seabrooke, will discuss their involvement in the Series, the cars, and the 2016 season.
